1 About

Michael: Alternative modeling to that about SmokCigNow + Packs_Year

  • Duration_Smoking + log_CigPerDaySmokAvg = Packs_Year
  • CigPerDaySmokNow (cont.) = SmokCigNow (binary)

2 Duration_Smoking + log_CigPerDaySmokAvg vs. Packs_Year

  • Model 1: . ~ . + ATS_PackYears
  • Model 2: . ~ . + Duration_Smoking + log_CigPerDaySmokAvg

3 CigPerDaySmokNow_gr

http://www.nhs.uk/news/2012/12December/Pages/Just-a-single-cigarette-a-day-linked-to-sudden-death.aspx

  • 1-14 cigarettes per day
  • 15-24 cigarettes per day
  • greater than or equal to 25 cigarettes per day
